{"about_the_game":"A huge crisis broke out in the Mirror-verse. In the name of justice (or probably mischief), the bishojos went to war! Select your heroine and fight! The mini-game collection of Mirror-verse: Mirror Party<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[GAMPLAY]</h2>There are currently 4 minigames, we plan to add as many as we can before the formal release.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/tank.gif?t=1638606649\" /><li>Tank Battlefield: No one can stop a trumping tank! Except for another tank. Wipe your opponents off of this earth, and earn some points along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/Leah1.gif?t=1638606649\" /><br></li><li>Leah's Secret Room: Leah has lost many of her stuff and she needs your help to find it. And of course, she's going to reward you... in her own way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/fireball.gif?t=1638606649\" /><br></li><li>Fireball Royale: Launch your mighty fireballs at your rivals and see what happens! Be careful of those poisonous fog, lightning, and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/farm.gif?t=1638606649\" /><br></li><li>Frenzy Farm: Who can resist the cute animals? But how about when they have gone frenzy! Contain them with the pumpkins!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">[GACHA MACHINE]</h2>Getting a little tired? I bet our 300+ collectibles can get you back. See those Gacha Tokens you got, put them in the Gacha Machine, and collect as many as you can. 100+ CGs, 100+ Cosplay Albums, Avatars for the Launcher, OST theme songs of Mirror Series.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787820/extras/gacha.gif?t=1638606649\" /><b